title: Key Flow: Transaction Lifecycle

user: "Dashboard User"
frontend: "Frontend Transaction Actions"
tx_api: "Transaction API"
tx_service: "Transaction Service"
session_gate: "Session and Symbol Checks"
session_state: "Session State Store"
tx_store: "Transaction Store"
snapshot_publisher: "Snapshot Publisher"
snapshot_topic: "Dashboard Snapshot Topic"

user -> frontend: clicks buy/short/sell/cover
frontend -> tx_api: posts open or close command
tx_api -> tx_service: validates and routes
tx_service -> session_gate: enforces open-session rules
tx_service -> session_state: reads latest symbol price
tx_service -> tx_store: writes transaction state
snapshot_publisher -> tx_store: reads transactions
snapshot_publisher -> snapshot_topic: publishes updated snapshot
frontend -> snapshot_topic: consumes updated transaction cards
